project-info.about:
Jakarta Activation lets you take advantage of standard services to: 
			determine the type of an arbitrary piece of data; encapsulate access to it; 
			discover the operations available on it;
			and instantiate the appropriate bean to perform the operation(s).
			Syncro Soft elects to include this software in this distribution under the EDL 1.0 license.
            You can obtain a copy of the original license at: https://www.eclipse.org/org/documents/edl-v10.php
